&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Tokyo" /><category term="Trains" /><category term="Golden Hour" /><summary type="html">Tokyo Station at golden hour. A 30 second exposure blurs most of the people taking selfies in front :-) マジックアワーの東京駅。30秒の露光で、前で自撮りする人たちのほとんどをぼかす。😀</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2210_A7R03331.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2210_A7R03331.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Komyo-in・光明院</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/221015/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Komyo-in・光明院" /><published>2022-10-15T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2022-10-15T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/komyo-in</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/221015/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
