&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Kyoto" /><category term="Kamo River" /><summary type="html">Beautiful sunny day in Kyoto. This is the glassy Kamo River, just above the Kamogawa Delta, where it merges with the Takano River. 京都の美しい晴れた日。これは鴨川デルタのすぐ上、高野川と合流するガラスのような鴨川です。</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2210_IMG_6149.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2210_IMG_6149.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Evening on the “O”・大川の夜</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/221012/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Evening on the “O”・大川の夜" /><published>2022-10-12T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2022-10-12T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/okawa</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/221012/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
